<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5290227>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3 a–d. Tetramelasma nodosatha sp. n. male. a, Habitus, in situ (scale bar = 2 mm); b, pygofer, dorsally; c, genital capsule, laterally; d, pygofer, ventrally (scale bar = 0.1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5290227/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5290229>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4 a–e. Tetramelasma nodosatha sp. n. male. a, Genital capsule, ventrally; b, genital capsule, laterally; c, style, posteroventrally, 5–6 teeth; d, style, posteroventrally, 1–2 teeth; e, aedeagus & connective, laterally (scale bar = 0.1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5290229/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5290231>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5a–f. Tetramelasma nodosatha sp. n. female. a, Habitus (scale bar = 2 mm); b–c, sternite 7, ventrally, in situ; d–f, sternite 7, ventrally (scale bar = 0.1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5290231/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5290235>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6a–l. Tetramelasma nodosatha sp. n. female. a, Habitus, submacropter; b, habitus, macropter (scale bar = 2 mm); c– g, sternite 7, ventrally; h, valvula 1; i, valvula 1 detail; j, valvula 2 detail; k, valvula 3; l, valvula 3 detail (scale bar = 0.1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5290235/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5290237>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7a–i. Tetramelasma scolosatha sp. n. male. a, Habitus (scale bar = 2 mm); b, pygofer, laterally; c, pygofer, ventrally; d, style, posteroventrally; e, aedeagus, laterally; f, aedeagus, dorsally; g, tegmina; h–i, hind wing (scale bar = 0.1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5290237/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

